description: '''Cute Is What We Aim For''' was an American [[pop-punk]] band from [[Buffalo, New York]]. Formed in 2005, they have released two albums: ''[[The Same Old Blood Rush with a New Touch]]'' (2006) and ''[[Rotation (Cute Is What We Aim For album)|Rotation]]'' (2008). They were signed to record label [[Fueled by Ramen]] for their two releases.
